download hadoop-2.9.1 from link below:
http://www.apache.org/dyn/closer.cgi/hadoop/common/hadoop-2.9.1/hadoop-2.9.1.tar.gz
make ssh-key access between all nodes.

after downloading and extracting go to the etc/hadoop and chage folowing file to defualt files:

masters
slaves
hadoop-env.sh
core-site.xml
hdfs-site.xml
mapred-site.xml
yarn-site.xml

after that insert following command :
bin/hdfs namenode -format